  }
+ Response 401 (application/json)

## 日記詳細 [/3.0/service/diaries/:id]

#### 日記の詳細取得[GET]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, required) - 日記ID
+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
  "id": 1,
  "authorID": 1111,
  "title": "志望企業が決められない",
  "body": "私はどこに向かっているのか",
  "likedCount": 3,
  "liked": false,
  "createdAt": "2019-09-02T16:16:22+09:00",
  "updatedAt": "2021-09-04T16:16:22+09:00"
  }

#### 日記の更新[PATCH]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, require) - 記事ID
    + title: (string, require) - タイトル
    + body: (string, require) - 本文
    + author_id: (number, require) - UserID

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
  "id": 1,
  "authorID": 1111,
  "title": "志望企業が決められない",
  "body": "決めるしか無い",
  "likedCount": 6,
  "liked": false,
  "createdAt": "2021-09-02T16:16:22+09:00",
  "updatedAt": "2021-09-07T16:16:22+09:00"
  }

#### 日記の削除[DELETE]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, require) - 記事ID
    + author_id: (number, require) - UserID
+ Response 204 (application/json)

## 日記へのいいね機能 [/3.0/service/diaries/{{@id}/like]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, require) - 記事ID
    + author_id: (number, require) - UserID
+ Response 204 (application/json)

### 指定された id の日記にいいねする[POST]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, require) - 記事ID
    + author_id: (number, require) - UserID
+ Response 204 (application/json)

### 指定された id の日記へのいいねを解除[DELETE]

+ Parameters
    + id: (number, require) - 記事ID
    + author_id: (number, require) - UserID
+ Response 204 (application/json)
